name: ARCH OF ADVENTURE
description: OUT THERE IN THE DESERT LIL PUP REALIZED THAT HIS LOVE OF ADVENTURE, CURIOSITY, AND DREAD OF MONOTONY—TRAITS INHERENT IN EVOLVING HUMAN NATURE—SUGGEST THAT DEATH IS ONLY THE BEGINNING OF AN ENDLESS CAREER OF ADVENTURE, AN EVERLASTING LIFE OF ANTICIPATION, AN ETERNAL VOYAGE OF DISCOVERY.
